      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "integral of sound energy density (<<t8-7>>) over a specified volume",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The sound energy in region stem:[\"R\"] can be expressed by:\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nQ = oint_\"R\" w(bb(ii(x)))\"d\"^3 bb(ii(x))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[\"d\"^3bb(ii(x))] is an element of volume.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
